  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package re-evaluates the COU at Model Risk Level 3 following an expanded regulatory submission scope. Thirteen credibility factors are addressed; twelve are fully assessed and meet or exceed required gradation levels. The 'Use error' factor is documented as not requiring formal assessment because the simulation workflow is executed by a single experienced analyst team with institutional SOPs—the assessment team judged this factor inapplicable to the COU, yet the factor record was filed with factorStatus 'not-assessed' rather than 'not-applicable', leaving a material credibility gap at MRL 3.",
