      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was performed following the Richardson extrapolation procedure. The grid convergence index (GCI) on the volume-averaged shear stress was 1.7%, well below the 5% threshold. Achieved gradation 3 exceeds the required gradation 2."
