      "rationale": "Bench-scale experiments were conducted at five flow-speed operating points matching the simulation boundary conditions. Blood analog fluid (glycerol-water mixture) viscosity and density were matched to physiological values within 3%. Achieved gradation 2 meets the required gradation 2."
    },
    {
