      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved gradation must meet or exceed required gradation for MRL 3.",
      "rationale": "Predicted relative hemolysis index (RH) was compared against measured values at all five operating points. Maximum normalized error was 8.4%, within the pre-specified 15% acceptance band. Achieved gradation 2 meets the required gradation 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
