      "rationale": "Validation experiments used the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under CPB-representative flow conditions. The validation domain closely matches the COU domain in geometry, fluid properties, and operating envelope. Achieved gradation 2 meets the required gradation 2."
    },
    {
