      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved gradation must meet or exceed required gradation for MRL 3.",
      "rationale": "Iterative convergence was confirmed by monitoring residuals to below 1e-6 and verifying mass imbalance below 0.01%. Double-precision arithmetic was used throughout. Achieved gradation 2 meets the required gradation 2."
    },
    {
