      "rationale": "The assessment team concluded that use error does not apply to this COU because the simulation workflow is executed exclusively by a small, experienced analyst team operating under institutional standard operating procedures, and no hand-off to untrained users is anticipated. Accordingly, no formal use-error assessment activity was conducted and no gradation was assigned. The factor record is filed as not-assessed."
    },
    {
