      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved gradation must meet or exceed required gradation for MRL 3.",
      "rationale": "The Reynolds-Averaged Navier-Stokes (RANS) k-omega SST turbulence model was selected based on published benchmark comparisons for rotating blood-contacting devices. Model-form assumptions (Newtonian blood analog, rigid walls) are consistent with the COU scope. Achieved gradation 2 meets the required gradation 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
