      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved gradation must meet or exceed required gradation for MRL 3.",
      "rationale": "Boundary conditions (inlet flow rate, rotational speed, outlet pressure) were derived from device specifications and clinical operating ranges. Fluid properties were measured at test temperature. Sensitivity of RH to ±5% variation in inlet flow was quantified and found to be within acceptable bounds. Achieved gradation 2 meets the required gradation 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
