      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved gradation must meet or exceed required gradation for MRL 3.",
      "rationale": "Three nominally identical pump specimens were tested; inter-specimen variability in measured RH was below 6%. Specimens were manufactured to drawing tolerances verified by CMM inspection. Achieved gradation 2 meets the required gradation 2."
